34
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,760
You want a comeback, right?

35
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:32,330
What does the baby have to do
with my comeback?

36
00:03:32,330 --> 00:03:33,660
Su Li has agreed to go

37
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:34,800
with an amicable divorce.

38
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,360
I can't believe you still trust her.

39
00:03:38,130 --> 00:03:39,360
Once the baby is born,

40
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,330
she's likely to use it to smear you

41
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:42,730
and ask you to pay child support.

42
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,300
You will be labeled

43
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:46,160
as abandoning your wife and child.

44
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:48,200
Your career will be ruined.

45
00:03:50,930 --> 00:03:51,730
Shuheng,

46
00:03:52,130 --> 00:03:53,400
if you like kids,

47
00:03:53,930 --> 00:03:55,260
we can have them later.

48
00:03:56,530 --> 00:03:58,600
You shouldn't let
Su Li's baby destroy your career.

49
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:00,800
Yes,

50
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,660
Yingying's right.

51
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:02,600
Shuheng,

52
00:04:03,060 --> 00:04:04,930
