53
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:05,860
You must be cautious.

54
00:04:09,060 --> 00:04:09,930
All right, I got it.

55
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,400
I will talk to her.

56
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:15,800
[Episode 9]
[Turn around in Time]

57
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:36,330
May I come in?

58
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:50,330
Thanks...

59
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:01,100
What's up?

60
00:05:01,860 --> 00:05:03,460
(We can't keep this baby.)

61
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:05,860
(You shouldn't let
Su Li's baby destroy your career.)

62
