After I knew you're pregnant,

63
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:10,930
I thought about it all night.

64
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,500
I think we should

65
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,100
get back together.

66
00:05:19,530 --> 00:05:22,330
You're weird enough.

67
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,500
This's

68
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:25,160
the funniest joke

69
