this Wednesday.

76
00:05:55,530 --> 00:05:56,330
You're right.

77
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,100
The baby needs a father,

78
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,960
but my baby's father

79
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,260
won't be you.

80
00:06:02,100 --> 00:06:04,460
I failed to find myself a good husband,

81
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,900
but I still hold the chance

82
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:09,600
to choose a good father for my next baby.

83
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:13,360
At least I've excluded a wrong answer.

84
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:15,300
Su Li,

85
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,500
please forgive me.

86
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:18,730
I swear

87
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,600
I'll be a good husband

88
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,960
and a good father.

89
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:23,860
Please give me a chance.

90
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:25,900
You really want to get back together?

91
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,930
I have a few

92
00:06:39,530 --> 00:06:40,300
small requests.

93
00:06:44,130 --> 00:06:44,660
Go ahead.

94
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,160
I'll fulfill them all.

95
00:06:47,930 --> 00:06:48,500
First,

96
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:51,260
we need to divorce first

97
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:51,860
and then remarry.

98
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,000
You leave with nothing in the divorce.

99
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,530
When we remarry,

100
00:06:56,530 --> 00:06:58,060
we need to sign a prenup

101
00:06:58,060 --> 00:06:59,660
that all the property belongs to me.

102
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,600
Second,

103
00:07:01,130 --> 00:07:03,730
I won't help with your work anymore

104
00:07:03,730 --> 00:07:04,360
and

105
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,460
you can't use my name

106
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:07,400
to get a job.

107
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:25,400
Do you still want

108
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,560
to be a good husband and father?

109
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,100
Wait,

110
00:07:44,530 --> 00:07:45,500
leave the key.

111
00:07:59,260 --> 00:07:59,730
How did it go?

112
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,300
You know

113
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:04,130
how Su Li's like.

114
00:08:05,660 --> 00:08:06,930
She refused to talk about the baby.

115
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,000
But luckily,

116
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:11,360
I convinced her.

117
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:12,630
This Wednesday,

118
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:13,860
she'll have the surgery.

119
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:35,530
Beauty,

120
00:08:35,530 --> 00:08:36,400
shall we make a friend?

121
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,600
Let's have fun together.

122
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,960
I have many friends.

123
00:08:45,100 --> 00:08:46,560
Well, do you need a boyfriend?

124
00:09:11,060 --> 00:09:11,960
Su Li.

125
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,800
Let me drive you home.

126
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:41,760
I don't want to go home.

127
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,300
Well,

128
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,660
come to my home tonight.

129
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:52,660
Su Li,

130
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:55,200
why don't ask me

131
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,300
what happened?

132
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,760
If you want to say,

133
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,200
you will tell me.

134
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:00,560
But if you don't,

135
00:10:01,130 --> 00:10:02,500
my asking won't help.

136
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:12,360
I asked my husband for a divorce.

137
00:10:13,530 --> 00:10:15,600
He suspected me of having an affair
with our neighbor upstairs.

138
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,530
He was drunk the other day,

139
00:10:17,530 --> 00:10:18,930
went upstairs and made a scene.

140
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:21,330
I can't bear him anymore,

141
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,530
so I told him I wanted a divorce.

142
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:25,760
At that moment,

143
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:27,700
I felt incredibly determined.

144
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:30,000
I've never displayed such an attitude
in my life.

145
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:34,660
But

146
00:10:35,730 --> 00:10:36,760
as time passed,

147
00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:41,300
I feel like

148
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,060
I've returned

149
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:44,060
to the weak

150
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:46,060
and indecisive me.

151
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,730
These days, I've been thinking a lot.

152
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,000
When we just got married,

153
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,900
he was actually very nice to me.

154
00:10:56,900 --> 00:10:58,860
But as his career grew,

155
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:03,330
he became colder to me.

156
00:11:07,860 --> 00:11:08,400
People

157
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:10,300
always change.

158
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,930
What's your plan now?

159
00:11:15,660 --> 00:11:16,860
I want a divorce,

160
00:11:19,060 --> 00:11:20,660
but I'm afraid to do that.

161
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:23,100
Don't care about what others say.

162
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:24,660
Some people

163
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:25,700
have mouths

164
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:27,130
but no brains.

165
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,760
As your friend,

166
00:11:30,660 --> 00:11:32,860
I hope you stay true to yourself.

167
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:35,160
Whatever decision you make,

168
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,160
I'll support you.

169
00:11:41,660 --> 00:11:42,400
Su Li,

170
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:45,500
I just sat there reflecting a lot.

171
00:11:45,930 --> 00:11:47,530
I've been living all these years,
but I feel like

172
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,860
I haven't achieved anything.

173
00:11:51,260 --> 00:11:53,700
The only thing I could be proud of,
my husband, is gone.

174
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:03,460
I feel like
I haven't experienced happiness yet

175
00:12:03,460 --> 00:12:05,260
and now I'm about to face unhappiness.

176
00:12:12,130 --> 00:12:14,100
I feel like my life's over.

177
00:12:16,730 --> 00:12:18,760
(Turn right at the intersection ahead.)

178
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,100
I really like

179
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:27,360
what the navigation app says.

180
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:30,900
(You've deviated from the route,)

181
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:33,200
(we've replanned the route for you.)

182
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:35,600
(Please make a U-turn
at a proper location.)

183
00:13:01,500 --> 00:13:02,500
Have a good rest

184
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,530
and don't overthink.

185
00:13:03,530 --> 00:13:04,700
Tomorrow, everything will be fine.

186
00:13:39,260 --> 00:13:45,300
[Reminder: Abortion Surgery on Wednesday]

187
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:31,700
Hurry up.

188
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:33,560
Why are we coming to the hospital?

189
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:35,200
Unless I see Su Li entering
the operating room,

190
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,600
I can't feel at ease.

191
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:37,960
I really need your company.

192
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,160
Doctor,

193
00:14:58,160 --> 00:15:02,660
please save my child.

194
00:15:02,660 --> 00:15:05,980
Doctor, save her!

195
00:15:05,980 --> 00:15:08,100
