198
00:15:11,570 --> 00:15:12,740
It's okay.

199
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,400
She's having severe bleeding.

200
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:17,640
Whose blood type is AB?

201
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:18,640
I'm not.

202
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:19,540
None of us.

203
00:15:20,570 --> 00:15:21,170
I am.

204
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:22,840
Me too.

205
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:25,740
You're pregnant.

206
00:15:25,740 --> 00:15:26,400
You, come with me.

207
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:34,300
If you feel uncomfortable,

208
00:15:34,300 --> 00:15:35,460
please let me know.

209
00:15:36,020 --> 00:15:36,940
Thank you.

210
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:40,720
How's it?

211
00:15:41,020 --> 00:15:41,620
Dizzy?

212
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:42,680
