221
00:16:06,420 --> 00:16:08,150
He'll grow stronger.

222
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:11,950
Although he looks small,

223
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:15,280
every baby entering this world

224
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:17,120
is embarking on a firm

225
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,320
and brave adventure.

226
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:28,550
(Did you see that?)

227
00:16:29,580 --> 00:16:30,520
(This's the embryo,)

228
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:31,350
(eight weeks old.)

229
00:16:33,980 --> 00:16:34,480
Ganggang.

230
00:16:34,950 --> 00:16:35,280
Hmm?

231
00:16:35,980 --> 00:16:36,920
Let's go.

232
00:16:39,180 --> 00:16:39,750
Where to?

233
00:16:41,780 --> 00:16:42,380
Home.

234
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:45,220
I decided to keep the child.

235
00:16:47,150 --> 00:16:47,920
I agree.

236
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:50,180
Let's go.

237
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:56,080
Su Li,

238
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:57,520
what do you want to do?

239
00:16:58,420 --> 00:16:59,980
You'd better keep your promise.

240
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:01,350
It's for the best of everyone.

241
00:17:01,350 --> 00:17:02,680
This baby is mine

242
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:04,280
and it has nothing to do with any of you.

243
00:17:07,220 --> 00:17:07,820
Su Li,

244
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:09,950
you selfish liar.

245
00:17:09,950 --> 00:17:11,220
I know you deserve no trust.

246
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:24,520
What's your plan for Su Li's child?

247
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,080
It's so urgent.

248
00:17:26,080 --> 00:17:27,620
You still have the mood
to read this lousy script?

249
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:31,980
A lousy script?

250
00:17:32,760 --> 00:17:33,760
If you are as capable as Su Li,

251
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:35,120
