252
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:36,960
What can I do

253
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:37,860
about Su Li's decision?

254
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,220
Don't be crazy around me.

255
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:41,760
I have to prepare for my audition.

256
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:43,760
I...

257
00:18:03,060 --> 00:18:03,920
Su Li.

258
00:18:05,420 --> 00:18:06,120
it's so early.

259
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:07,260
Where are we going?

260
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:10,920
Last night, I made this,

261
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,790
a plan throughout my pregnancy.

262
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:13,660
Have a look.

263
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,760
So we have so many things to do today.

264
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:19,920
We need to leave early.

265
00:18:20,380 --> 00:18:21,420
[Pregnancy Plan]

266
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:22,320
Su Li,

267
00:18:22,790 --> 00:18:25,390
you just decided
to keep this baby yesterday,

268
00:18:25,390 --> 00:18:26,760
but today, you've already decided

269
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:27,520
which school he'll go to

270
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:29,590
after his birth.

271
00:18:29,860 --> 00:18:31,420
Since I've decided to keep him,

272
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:32,760
I must give him the best.

273
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:35,620
Let's go.

274
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:38,790
This is the luxurious VIP suite
in our hospital.

275
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:39,760
Our meals are all provided

276
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:41,790
by a five-star hotel.

277
00:18:42,320 --> 00:18:44,620
Medical staff are on call 24 hours a day.

278
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:47,820
Your delivery process will be operated
by our president,

279
00:18:47,820 --> 00:18:51,160
the former chief physician of
a Three-A hospital.

280
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,190
I reserve it.

281
00:18:54,190 --> 00:18:55,160
And this,

282
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:56,190
this one,

283
00:18:57,320 --> 00:18:57,990
this

284
00:18:58,920 --> 00:18:59,620
and that red one,

285
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:01,260
this

286
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,020
and that one.

287
00:19:04,020 --> 00:19:04,790
I'll take it all.

288
00:19:10,820 --> 00:19:11,760
Su Li,

289
00:19:11,760 --> 00:19:12,990
give it to me.

290
00:19:12,990 --> 00:19:13,920
You sit down.

291
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:14,860
